# Scientific Calculator

A web-based **Scientific Calculator** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It supports basic arithmetic operations as well as advanced functions like square, square root, inverse, power, trigonometric functions (sin, cos, tan), and logarithm.

